 said to then secretly display its prey."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Legends in snowy regions say that a woman who was lost on an icy mountain was reborn as FROSLASS."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Legends in snowy regions say that a woman who was lost on an icy mountain was reborn as FROSLASS"},{"version":"black","text":"It freezes prey by blowing its -58 degrees F breath. It is said to then secretly display its prey."},{"version":"white","text":"It freezes prey by blowing its -58 degrees F breath. It is said to then secretly display its prey."},{"version":"black-2","text":"It freezes prey by blowing its -58 degrees F breath. It is said to then secretly display its prey."},{"version":"white-2","text":"It freezes prey by blowing its -58 degrees F breath. It is said to then secretly display its prey."},{"version":"x","text":"It freezes foes with an icy breath nearly -60 degrees Fahrenheit. What seems to be its body is actually hollow."},{"version":"y","text":"Legends in snowy regions say that a woman who was lost on an icy mountain was reborn as Froslass."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"It freezes foes with an icy breath nearly -60 degrees Fahrenheit. What seems to be its body is actually hollow."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Legends in snowy regions say that a woman who was lost on an icy mountain was reborn as Froslass."},{"version":"sun","text":"When it finds humans or Pok\u00e9mon it likes, it freezes them and takes them to its chilly den, where they become decorations."},{"version":"moon","text":"The soul of a woman lost on a snowy mountain possessed an icicle, becoming this Pok\u00e9mon. The food it most relishes is the souls of men."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It freezes hikers who have come to climb snowy mountains and carries them back to its home. It only goes after men it thinks are handsome."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It\u2019s said that on nights of terrible blizzards, it comes down to human settlements. If you hear it knocking at your door, do not open it!"},{"version":"sword","text":"After a woman met her end on a snowy mountain, her regrets lingered on. From them, this Pok\u00e9mon was born. Its favorite food is frozen souls."},{"version":"shield","text":"It spits out cold air of nearly \u221260 degrees Fahrenheit to freeze its quarry. It brings frozen prey back to its lair and neatly lines them up."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"A Pok\u00e9mon inhabited by the soul of a woman who died bearing a grudge in the snowy mountains. Legends of Froslass placing deathly curses on misbehaving men send shivers down my spine."}],"evo":{"name":"snorunt","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"glalie","level":1,"min_level":42,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]},{"name":"froslass","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"use-item","item":"dawn-stone","held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/478.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/478.png","capture":75,"happiness":70,"growth":"medium","gender":8,"hatch":20,"ev":{"speed":2},"forms":[{"id":10285,"name":"froslass-mega","sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/10285.png"}]}